title: Rihanna's Stand Out Vetements x Canada Goose Camouflage Look

organizations.name: vetements x canada goose camouflage look rihanna

text: Rihanna Stands Out in Full Winter Camo February 7, 2017 4:58 PM by Marjon Carlos Photo: Splash News While Rihanna could never recede into the background, at least the style chameleon attempted to blend into her natural surroundings last night. Out and about in the concrete jungle that is New York, Rihanna zipped into an all-over camo look that was ready for any terrain. To match her oversize Vetements x Canada Goose camouflage-printed parka, which shielded her from the winter winds, the singer paired her gargantuan topper with a pair of slouchy cargo pants splashed in the same tonal print. Snuggled up into a Champion gray knit, she flung the hoodie over her head, heightening the sense of mystery around her look. Still, Rihanna’s accessories were major standouts. Although her gray Balenciaga ankle-strap Mary Janes and Céline luggage handbag blended into her ensemble, they also elevated the rugged look and imbued its tomboyishness with a sense of glamor and femininity.
